1) Create folders:
 test1dMpi-explicit  test1dMpi-implicit  test2dMpi
for saving files

2) Solve eqs
1D:
change method to "implicit" or "explicit" in solve1Dmpi.py
mpirun -n 4 python3 solve1Dmpi.py
2D:
nprocx=2 and nprocy=2 hardcoded in solve2Dmpi.py (nprocx * nprocy must be equal to  the total number of processes)
mpirun -n 4 python3 solve2Dmpi.py

3)Plot
1D:
change outdir in plotSol1d.py for expl/impl
python3 plotSol1d.py 
2D:
python3 plotSol2d.py

